-------------[ Itinerary  - Heritage, Hills & Horizons ]-------------

# Day 01 – Arrival in Colombo → Negombo Beach

Arrive at Bandaranaike International Airport and transfer to the coastal town of Negombo.

Highlights
• Relax at Negombo Beach
• Sunset at Negombo Browns Beach
• Optional lagoon boat ride at Negombo Lagoon

Overnight: Beachfront hotel – Negombo

---

# Day 02 – Ancient Anuradhapura Kingdom

Travel to the sacred city of Anuradhapura.

Highlights
• Sri Maha Bodhi
• Ruwanwelisaya
• Jetavanaramaya
• Kuttam Pokuna Twin Ponds

Overnight: Lakefront hotel – Anuradhapura

---

# Day 03 – Journey to Northern Sri Lanka (Jaffna)

Travel to the cultural heart of the north, Jaffna.

Highlights
• Jaffna Fort
• Nallur Kandaswamy Temple
• Explore vibrant local markets and cuisine

Overnight: Jaffna hotel

---

# Day 04 – Jaffna Peninsula & Island Culture

Highlights
• Nagadeepa Purana Vihara
• Keerimalai Natural Springs
• Relax at Casuarina Beach

Optional: Visit remote Delft Island.

Overnight: Jaffna

---

# Day 05 – East Coast Escape: Trincomalee

Travel to the beautiful eastern coastal city of Trincomalee.

Highlights
• Koneswaram Temple
• Trincomalee Harbour
• Beach relaxation at Nilaveli Beach

Overnight: Beach resort – Trincomalee

---

# Day 06 – Sigiriya Rock Fortress Adventure

Travel inland to the legendary Sigiriya Rock Fortress.

Highlights
• Climb the famous Lion Rock
• Fresco paintings & mirror wall
• Optional sunset hike at Pidurangala Rock

Overnight: Nature resort – Sigiriya

---

# Day 07 – Dambulla → Cultural Capital Kandy

Visit the golden cave temples of Dambulla.

Highlights
• Dambulla Cave Temple
• Spice garden experience
• Scenic drive to Kandy

Evening
• Temple of the Sacred Tooth Relic
• Traditional Kandyan cultural dance show

Overnight: Kandy hotel

---

# Day 08 – Kandy Cultural Exploration

Highlights
• Royal Botanical Gardens Peradeniya
• Kandy Lake
• Kandy View Point

Free evening for shopping and cafes.

Overnight: Kandy

---

# Day 09 – Pinnawala Elephants & Colombo City

Travel towards Colombo.

Highlights
• Pinnawala Elephant Orphanage
• Gangaramaya Temple
• Colombo Lotus Tower
• Sunset walk at Galle Face Green

Overnight: Colombo

---

# Day 10 – Departure

Breakfast at hotel.

Transfer to Bandaranaike International Airport for your departure flight.

Farewell Sri Lanka — until we meet again.





